{"tid":2463742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國足協譴責Nike「錯誤行徑」 稱保留處理合約權利","createTime":"2021-03-27T02:59:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T05:02:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"7935b9464546eea23f7dbb21e70a1374f4c75e8d","tid":2463742,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:59:09.000Z","msg":"報道指出，不論是中超還是國家隊，都與Nike有長約在身，雖然雙方保持了長期的商業合作關係，但認為觸及到「國家尊嚴民族團結大局」，就沒有任何轉彎的餘地。<br />\n<br />\n「新疆棉事件爆發以來，中國足協和職業聯盟籌備組高度關注，並緊急就此事召開了內部會議，對耐克公司（Nike）在棉花原料選擇上的錯誤行徑表達了譴責。對於耐克此番的錯誤行徑，無論是中國足協還是職業聯盟籌備組，都將保留進一步處理同耐克合同的權力。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210327/VZJFMMUNHBGXJAB3XOJSWU2JIY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210327%2FVZJFMMUNHBGXJAB3XOJSWU2JIY%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=50cba52f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20210327%2FVZJFMMUNHBGXJAB3XOJSWU2JIY%2F&h=c2d4b7fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/sports/20210327/VZJFMMUNHBGXJAB3XOJSWU2JIY/</a>"},{"pid":"67fc1995401bd5da975c7a6478d736853d0f5164","tid":2463742,"uid":20870,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T02:59:58.000Z","msg":"講咁多 解左約先啦"},{"pid":"52cc9cbf18fdedf848e6a1b44a0f2b9e8f5522e6","tid":2463742,"uid":28068,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"中國足協保留追究權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n罰番nike轉頭"},{"pid":"fdd41255f9b7d54611fc43d58c866ee268644b02","tid":2463742,"uid":10338,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T03:03:22.000Z","msg":"收到風<br />\n支足已經準備杯葛卡塔爾世界盃<br />\n唔會參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為根本入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" cl